      <title>音乐播放器安装配置</title>
      <link href="/2023/09/29/%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
      <url>/2023/09/29/%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[    <div id="aplayer-OMYKziZs" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker"         data-id="436346833" data-server="netease" data-type="song" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="false" data-mutex="true" data-listmaxheight="1000px" data-preload="auto" data-theme="#555"    ></div><hr><h1>音乐播放器安装配置</h1><h2 id="全局吸底Aplayer">全局吸底Aplayer</h2><ol><li><p>在’_config.yaml’底下添加如下代码：</p> <figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">aplayer:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">asset_inject:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在’_config.butterfly.yaml’中找到aplayerInject: 修改为如下：</p> <figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">aplayerInject:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">per_page:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>将Aplayer代码插入到主题配置文件：</p> <figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">inject:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">head:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">bottom:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&lt;div</span> <span class="string">class=&quot;aplayer</span> <span class="literal">no</span><span class="string">-destroy&quot;</span> <span class="string">data-id=&quot;8761921957&quot;</span> <span class="string">data-server=&quot;netease&quot;</span> <span class="string">data-type=&quot;playlist&quot;</span> <span class="string">data-fixed=&quot;true&quot;</span> <span class="string">data-order=&quot;random&quot;</span> <span class="string">data-mutex=&quot;true&quot;&gt;</span> <span class="string">&lt;/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 注意：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 1. data-id 参数为音乐播放器ID，在音乐播放器中查看</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 2. data-server 参数为音乐平台，目前支持：netease、tencent、kugou、xiami、baidu，默认为 netease</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 3. data-type 参数为音乐类型，目前支持：song、playlist、album、search，默认为 song; 且必须与提供id的实际类型一致，否则无法显示播放器</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 4. 实际操作中发现 data-autoplay:&quot;true&quot; 并不生效，暂且不知为何。</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更多参数说明请参考： <a href="https://github.com/MoePlayer/hexo-tag-aplayer">hexo-tag-aplayer的Github文档</a></p><ul><li><font size=4><em><strong>至此，全局音乐插件的配置就完成了</strong></em></font></li></ul></li></ol><h2 id="文章内音乐插件的配置">文章内音乐插件的配置</h2><ol><li><p>在文章中插入音乐代码：</p>   <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% meting &quot;436346833&quot; &quot;netease&quot; &quot;song&quot; &quot;theme:#555&quot; &quot;mutex:true&quot; &quot;listmaxheight:1000px&quot; &quot;preload:auto&quot; %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>我还没有搞明白Front-matter中参数aplayer的作用，可以不填，也可以填为: true；目前来说都能够实现页面播放器。</p></li></ol><ul><li><font size=4><em><strong>至此，文章内的音乐播放器插件也配置好了</strong></em></font></li></ul><hr><h1>所应用的额外知识</h1><ul><li><p>这里记录一下文字链接的编写方式：</p><ol><li><p>html：</p> <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">更多参数说明请参考： <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://github.com/MoePlayer/hexo-tag-aplayer&quot;</span>&gt;</span>hexo-tag-aplayer的Github文档<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">使用<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span>标签将需要设置链接的文字括在内，并使用href指定跳转页面</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>markdown：</p> <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">更多参数说明请参考：[<span class="string">hexo-tag-aplayer的Github文档</span>](<span class="link">https://github.com/MoePlayer/hexo-tag-aplayer &quot;hexo-tag-aplayer的github官方页&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">使用[<span class="string">被设置链接的文字</span>](<span class="link">链接网址 &quot;鼠标悬停时显示的说明信息&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol></li><li><p>这里记录一下尾部标记所用的html语法</p> <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    &lt;center&gt;&lt;/center&gt;标签表示居中显示</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    &lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;标签表示粗体显示</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    &lt;i&gt;&lt;/i&gt;标签表示斜体显示</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    &lt;font color=xxx size=3&gt;&lt;/font&gt;标签表示利用color属性设置字体颜色，size属性设置字体大小(值为1-7)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#FF0000</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">3</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">                明日君再来</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><hr><p>这篇文章创建于：04:38:41，目前时间为：06:59:15。<br>•ࡇ•|||<br>妈耶，希望能越来越熟练吧，那就先到这！</p><center>    <b>        <i>            <font color=#FF0000 size=3>                明日君再来            </font>        </i>    </b> </center>]]></content>
      
      
